		<br><br>
		<%= @sitename %> is a NO-CODE information manager that allows you to create
		collections of business objects (e.g., Clients, Interventions, Technicians, Expenses, Projects, etc.),
		link them (Clients <=> Interventions <=> Technicians <=> Expenses),
		and securely share them online with your collaborators.
	</p>

	<h4 class="mb-2">Project Management</h4>
	<p class="fs-5 fw-light w-sm-75">
		Are you responsible for a team and the successful execution of a project program?
		<br><br>
		<%= @sitename %> allows you to quickly create a tool for tracking the status
		of each project without writing a single line of code.
		You’ll be notified when a significant status change is recorded,
		and you can view your deadlines in a 'Calendar'
		view or in your personal agenda (Google Calendar/Outlook/etc.).
	</p>

