		Are you looking for a simple tool to manage your files, documents, reports, and information collected in the field?
		<br><br>
		<%= @sitename %> was designed to be usable on a smartphone to collect data as close to its source as possible, regardless of its type (Text, Numbers, Photo, PDF, etc.).
		Contextual data, such as weather conditions and GPS location, can be automatically acquired.
		A graph generation tool allows you to visualize the information in the form of a curve or a histogram.
	</p>

